	(text_box "The antenna feed line from the module's ANT pin to the antenna should be matched to 50 Ω.\n\nThe target resonant frequency is in the LTE band 20 (800 MHz).\n\nProvide a footprint for a Π-type matching network for later tuning."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 255.27 50.8 0)
		(size 73.66 38.1)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
